result.name: Abhisar Garg
result.bio: Abhisar Garg is a software engineer. He completed his engineering from IMS Engineering College, Ghaziabad. He is presently working with Wells Fargo. Before that he worked for Synechron, a New York based firm for 6 Years. He has worked for HCL for a couple of years too. He is also a freelance developer and graphic designer. He is an aspiring writer and really passionate about it. Writing has always interested him. He truly believes “Writing comes from heart, even better from a broken heart”. He started his writing from poems. He participated in many poetry competitions and has also bagged prizes for his work. His recent works have also been published with renowned publishers. Photography is his another liking. He started photography in the 1st year of engineering and is exploring more avenues. With photography he has developed his skills in graphic designing. Abhisar is a multi-tasker. He wants to know, learn and do everything in his life. He is taking steps to do so. With his start-up ‘MotivTech India’, selected in top 300 start-ups of India, he wants to spread the tech knowledge among the masses providing them with great support and expertise. He acts as a game changer and is trying his best to make a difference. Catch him on www.abhisar.in to know more about this young man.
